OL,3,CJoey Barton in court charged with
OL,4,Csending offensive messages
OL,6,FFormer footballer Joey Barton has
OL,7,Fappeared in court charged with sending
OL,8,Foffensive messages on social media to
OL,9,Fa commentator and a radio presenter.
OL,11,FBarton, 42, faced Chester Magistrates'
OL,12,FCourt by videolink charged with two
OL,13,Fcounts of sending communications of an
OL,14,Findecent/offensive nature to Lucy Ward
OL,15,Fand Jeremy Vine.
OL,17,FHe had been due to appear in person
OL,18,Fbut Richard Derby, defending, said he
OL,19,Fwas unable to attend as he had not
OL,20,Fbeen made aware of the date and was
OL,21,F"minding the children".
