OL,3,CJoey Barton in court charged with
OL,4,Csending offensive messages
OL,6,FBarton is alleged to have sent
OL,7,Fmessages to former England footballer
OL,8,FWard between 3 and 8 January 2024, and
OL,9,Fto Vine between 9 January and 20 March
OL,10,F2024.
OL,12,FThe messages were of an indecent or
OL,13,Fgrossly offensive nature for the
OL,14,Fpurpose of causing distress and
OL,15,Fanxiety, the charges state.
OL,17,FBarton, of Widnes, Cheshire, confirmed
OL,18,Fhe was indicating not guilty pleas to
OL,19,Fboth offences.
