OL,3,CJoey Barton in court charged with
OL,4,Csending offensive messages
OL,6,FThe case was sent to Liverpool Crown
OL,7,FCourt, where Barton is due to stand
OL,8,Ftrial in May accused of sending
OL,9,Fmalicious communications to football
OL,10,Fpundit Eni Aluko.
OL,12,FBarton tweeted after Aluko and Ward
OL,13,Fappeared as pundits on ITV for an FA
OL,14,FCup match between Crystal Palace and
OL,15,FEverton on 4 January 2024, allegedly
OL,16,Fcomparing them to serial killers Fred
OL,17,Fand Rose West.
OL,19,FIn a follow-up tweet, he compared
OL,20,FAluko to Joseph Stalin and Pol Pot, an
OL,21,Fearlier court hearing was told.
